      • handleAction

        protected boolean handleAction(java.awt.event.ActionEvent e)
        Description copied from class: ExportArchiveAction
        This method will set up the SaveKAR object in the case of saving a workflow. To save other types of KARs a subclass that overrides this method can be used to add multiple workflows to the SaveKAR object and to identify other objects that should be added to the KAR through the appropriate KAREntryHandlers.
        Overrides:
        handleAction in class ExportArchiveAction
        Returns:
        boolean true if the export should continue
